---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import ProcessSteps from '../components/ProcessSteps.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const title = "Tire Dressing Fort Lauderdale | Mobile Service | Route95";
const description = "Professional tire dressing in Fort Lauderdale. Long-lasting shine, UV protection, non-sling formula. Mobile service - we come to you! Call 754-215-2272";

const parentCategory = {
  href: `${base}car-wash-fort-lauderdale/`,
  title: "Car Wash Services"
};
---

<ServiceLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  h1="Tire Dressing Fort Lauderdale"
  intro="Professional tire dressing gives your tires a rich, dark finish while protecting them from Florida's intense UV rays, salt air, and road grime."
  currentPage="/tire-dressing-fort-lauderdale/"
  parentCategory={parentCategory}
>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
      <section>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Your tires are constantly exposed to the elements. In Fort Lauderdale, that means relentless UV radiation, salt air from the ocean, humidity, and hot pavement. Without protection, rubber dries out, cracks, and develops that faded brown look that makes even clean cars look neglected.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Most tire dressings from auto parts stores look good for a day, then sling onto your fenders or wash off in the first rain. Cheap dressings can actually damage tires by containing petroleum distillates that dry out rubber over time.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We use Chemical Guys VRP (Vinyl, Rubber, Plastic) and premium water-based tire dressings that condition rubber while providing a deep, dark finish that lasts. Our mobile service brings professional tire dressing directly to your Fort Lauderdale location.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">How Much Does Tire Dressing Cost in Fort Lauderdale?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Professional tire dressing in Fort Lauderdale costs $25 to $40 for all four tires.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Standard applications fall at the lower end. Heavily oxidized or neglected tires requiring extra cleaning and multiple coats cost more. The service includes tire sidewall cleaning before dressing application.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">How Long Does Tire Dressing Take?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Tire dressing takes 10 to 15 minutes for all four tires when added to a wash or detail service.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          As a standalone service, allow 20-30 minutes since we need to properly clean the sidewalls first. Dressing applied to dirty tires won't bond properly and won't last.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">Why Professional Tire Dressing Matters in South Florida</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Fort Lauderdale's climate is brutal on tires. UV radiation, salt air, and humidity cause premature aging that proper dressing prevents.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Problems caused by unprotected tires:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Brown, faded appearance from UV oxidation</li>
          <li>Dry rot and sidewall cracking</li>
          <li>Rubber becomes brittle and loses flexibility</li>
          <li>Reduced tire lifespan</li>
          <li>Your entire car looks older and neglected</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Florida sun can fade tires within weeks of installation. Regular dressing maintains that showroom-black appearance and extends tire life.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-6">Our Tire Dressing Process</h2>
        <ProcessSteps steps={[
          { title: "Tire Cleaning", description: "We scrub sidewalls with degreaser to remove old dressing, road grime, and browning. Clean rubber bonds with dressing properly." },
          { title: "Rinse and Dry", description: "Thorough rinse removes all degreaser. We dry the sidewall surface so dressing adheres properly without dilution." },
          { title: "Dressing Application", description: "We apply Chemical Guys tire dressing with an applicator pad, working it into the rubber for even coverage." },
          { title: "Excess Removal", description: "We wipe away excess product to prevent sling. The dressing should absorb into rubber, not sit on top waiting to fling onto your paint." },
          { title: "Cure Time", description: "We allow the dressing to cure before you drive. This ensures maximum durability and prevents transfer to your fenders." }
        ]} />
      </section>
    </div>

    <aside class="lg:col-span-1">
      <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">Tire Dressing Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-[#c0c7cf] font-bold">$</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600">$25-$40 for all four</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c0c7cf] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">10-15 minutes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c0c7cf] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">UV protection</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c0c7cf] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Non-sling formula</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c0c7cf] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Lasts 2-4 weeks</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#0f2a4a] rounded-xl p-6 text-white">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">Book Tire Dressing</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
            Same-day appointments available throughout Fort Lauderdale.
          </p>
          <a href="tel:+17542152272" class="btn-accent w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
            754-215-2272
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">Related Services</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href={`${base}wheel-cleaning-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Wheel Cleaning</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}trim-restoration-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Trim Restoration</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}hand-wash-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Hand Wash</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}full-detail-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Full Detail</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>
